Class Teleporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • cells.Cell
      • cells.Teleporter

  • public class Teleporter
extends Cell
    The class for the cell type Teleporter. It will store a Vector for both itself and a linked Teleporter. Will also hold the information for rendering
